  #data-viz-dave-columbus
    %h3.title
      %a{href:'/events.html#data-viz-dave-columbus'}Oct 15th 2015: Data Visualizations with Dave Columbus
    %p
      Dave Columbus will take us on an adventure of graphic proportions. He has spent years collecting and organizing data about pop culture and creating visual arts. His visualizations express truths and debunk common myths about our favorite television shows and movies.

    %p Dave will give us a survey of how data visualizations are constructed and the many different ways data can be displayed. This will cover generating static non-interactive works and his current exploration of dynamic interactive visualizations.

    %p It is going to be great fun. The format will be a presentation and then QA / group driven discussion.

